COPY public.eval_criteria (id, key, name, description, category, score_type, severity, weight, active, sort_order, created_at, updated_at, project_id) FROM stdin;
2bbe1c33-e8d7-419b-8197-11e284036604	no_unauthorized_advice	No unauthorised investment advice	The broker must not give unsolicited investment advice, price predictions, or buy/sell recommendations. Factual information (current price, order status, product features) is allowed. Fail if the broker volunteers recommendations or predictions.	compliance	pass_fail	critical	2	t	3	2026-06-12 11:39:10.979889+00	2026-06-12 11:39:10.979889+00	00000000-0000-0000-0000-0000000000d1
c3690474-2627-46fd-bcc4-052def24cc39	risk_disclosure	Risk disclosure where required	If the client asks for an opinion, or the order involves derivatives or leveraged products, the broker must give an appropriate risk warning. For plain equity orders where no advice is sought, this criterion passes by default.	compliance	pass_fail	warning	1	t	4	2026-06-12 11:39:10.979889+00	2026-06-12 11:39:10.979889+00	00000000-0000-0000-0000-0000000000d1
a1513d39-af5c-45ae-a904-7272d1a4a324	professional_conduct	Professional conduct	The broker is courteous and professional throughout: a proper greeting identifying the firm, polite tone, no over-familiarity that compromises professionalism, and a proper closing. Score 1 (poor) to 5 (exemplary).	quality	scale_1_5	info	1	t	5	2026-06-12 11:39:10.979889+00	2026-06-12 11:39:10.979889+00	00000000-0000-0000-0000-0000000000d1
db72683f-1952-4a74-b349-fafac61ca879	identity_verification	Client identity verified	Identity must be established before the first order is accepted: the client states (or the broker actively confirms) the client's name AND an account number or account suffix. It counts whether the client volunteers this or the broker asks for it. Fail only when no name/account is stated by anyone before the order — e.g. the broker recognises the caller's voice and proceeds.	compliance	pass_fail	critical	2	t	1	2026-06-12 11:39:10.979889+00	2026-06-12 11:45:12.463853+00	00000000-0000-0000-0000-0000000000d1
e3cbfe87-0de5-4fed-9632-0fac46611d00	order_readback	Order read back and confirmed	Before submitting each order the broker must read back the order details — stock, side, quantity, and price (or market order) — and obtain the client's confirmation. The transcript is ASR-generated and may garble words and digits: if a read-back clearly occurred (the broker repeats the order and asks for confirmation), count it as performed even when individual digits or words differ from the client's request; note such discrepancies in the rationale instead of failing. Fail only when an order was accepted with no read-back at all.	compliance	pass_fail	critical	2	t	2	2026-06-12 11:39:10.979889+00	2026-06-12 11:45:12.48365+00	00000000-0000-0000-0000-0000000000d1
10381215-a7b8-4a0b-8217-1c4ec1b94929	greeting_and_branding	Greeting and Branding	Check if the agent greets the customer professionally and explicitly states the online store's name within the first 10 seconds of the call.	compliance	pass_fail	warning	1	t	0	2026-06-15 09:03:14.207058+00	2026-06-15 09:03:14.207058+00	10f1c025-065e-47f9-ab16-bbe98bb09f95
2a389652-962f-4e2e-9823-c072c5b6d28f	customer_verification	Customer and Order Verification	Verify that the agent confirms the customer's identity, order number, or account details before discussing specific order details.	compliance	pass_fail	critical	3	t	0	2026-06-15 09:03:14.226906+00	2026-06-15 09:03:14.226906+00	10f1c025-065e-47f9-ab16-bbe98bb09f95
59401c25-51a1-48df-9d74-0a3b22206357	issue_resolution_escalation	Issue Resolution or Escalation	Evaluate whether the agent successfully resolved the customer's inquiry or followed the correct escalation procedure if a resolution was not immediately possible.	quality	scale_1_5	critical	3	t	0	2026-06-15 09:03:14.24595+00	2026-06-15 09:03:14.24595+00	10f1c025-065e-47f9-ab16-bbe98bb09f95
8b918f15-2023-47db-9c00-3031cd3a18c5	empathy_and_listening	Empathy and Active Listening	Assess how well the agent demonstrated empathy, listened actively without interrupting, and acknowledged the customer's feelings or frustration.	quality	scale_1_5	warning	2	t	0	2026-06-15 09:03:14.262919+00	2026-06-15 09:03:14.262919+00	10f1c025-065e-47f9-ab16-bbe98bb09f95
