ent asks for an opinion, or the order involves derivatives or leveraged products, the broker must give an appropriate risk warning. For plain equity orders where no advice is sought, this criterion passes by default."}, {"key": "professional_conduct", "name": "Professional conduct", "weight": 1.0, "category": "quality", "severity": "info", "score_type": "scale_1_5", "description": "The broker is courteous and professional throughout: a proper greeting identifying the firm, polite tone, no over-familiarity that compromises professionalism, and a proper closing. Score 1 (poor) to 5 (exemplary)."}]	[{"key": "stock_code", "label": "Stock code", "scope": "trade", "field_type": "string", "enum_options": null}, {"key": "stock_name", "label": "Stock name", "scope": "trade", "field_type": "string", "enum_options": null}, {"key": "side", "label": "Side", "scope": "trade", "field_type": "enum", "enum_options": ["buy", "sell", "amend", "cancel", "unknown"]}, {"key": "quantity", "label": "Quantity", "scope": "trade", "field_type": "number", "enum_options": null}, {"key": "price", "label": "Price", "scope": "trade", "field_type": "number", "enum_options": null}, {"key": "price_type", "label": "Price type", "scope": "trade", "field_type": "enum", "enum_options": ["market", "limit", "unknown"]}, {"key": "client_name", "label": "Client name", "scope": "trade", "field_type": "string", "enum_options": null}, {"key": "client_account", "label": "Client account", "scope": "trade", "field_type": "string", "enum_options": null}, {"key": "call_purpose", "label": "Call purpose", "scope": "call", "field_type": "enum", "enum_options": ["place_order", "amend_or_cancel", "inquiry", "complaint", "other"]}, {"key": "complaint_mentioned", "label": "Complaint mentioned", "scope": "call", "field_type": "boolean", "enum_options": null}]	The client called to inquire about their account balance and how to subscribe to an upcoming IPO next week. The broker explained that the account balance can be checke