ent asks for an opinion, or the order involves derivatives or leveraged products, the broker must give an appropriate risk warning. For plain equity orders where no advice is sought, this criterion passes by default."}, {"key": "professional_conduct", "name": "Professional conduct", "weight": 1.0, "category": "quality", "severity": "info", "score_type": "scale_1_5", "description": "The broker is courteous and professional throughout: a proper greeting identifying the firm, polite tone, no over-familiarity that compromises professionalism, and a proper closing. Score 1 (poor) to 5 (exemplary)."}]	[{"key": "stock_code", "label": "Stock code", "scope": "trade", "field_type": "string", "enum_options": null}, {"key": "stock_name", "label": "Stock name", "scope": "trade", "field_type": "string", "enum_options": null}, {"key": "side", "label": "Side", "scope": "trade", "field_type": "enum", "enum_options": ["buy", "sell", "amend", "cancel", "unknown"]}, {"key": "quantity", "label": "Quantity", "scope": "trade", "field_type": "number", "enum_options": null}, {"key": "price", "label": "Price", "scope": "trade", "field_type": "number", "enum_options": null}, {"key": "price_type", "label": "Price type", "scope": "trade", "field_type": "enum", "enum_options": ["market", "limit", "unknown"]}, {"key": "client_name", "label": "Client name", "scope": "trade", "field_type": "string", "enum_options": null}, {"key": "client_account", "label": "Client account", "scope": "trade", "field_type": "string", "enum_options": null}, {"key": "call_purpose", "label": "Call purpose", "scope": "call", "field_type": "enum", "enum_options": ["place_order", "amend_or_cancel", "inquiry", "complaint", "other"]}, {"key": "complaint_mentioned", "label": "Complaint mentioned", "scope": "call", "field_type": "boolean", "enum_options": null}]	The client, Mr. Li, called to place two trade orders: to buy 5,000 shares of HSBC (00005) at a limit price of 102.5, and to sell 20,000 shares of Xiaomi (01810) at mar