bca598a2-1964-4a96-965b-7734ea4bed0c	1c674f76-57cf-4f5b-903b-b28cb66d0733	9	completed	gemini-3.5-flash	[{"key": "identity_verification", "name": "Client identity verified", "weight": 2.0, "category": "compliance", "severity": "critical", "score_type": "pass_fail", "description": "Identity must be established before the first order is accepted: the client states (or the broker actively confirms) the client's name AND an account number or account suffix. It counts whether the client volunteers this or the broker asks for it. Fail only when no name/account is stated by anyone before the order — e.g. the broker recognises the caller's voice and proceeds."}, {"key": "order_readback", "name": "Order read back and confirmed", "weight": 2.0, "category": "compliance", "severity": "critical", "score_type": "pass_fail", "description": "Before submitting each order the broker must read back the order details — stock, side, quantity, and price (or market order) — and obtain the client's confirmation. The transcript is ASR-generated and may garble words and digits: if a read-back clearly occurred (the broker repeats the order and asks for confirmation), count it as performed even when individual digits or words differ from the client's request; note such discrepancies in the rationale instead of failing. Fail only when an order was accepted with no read-back at all."}, {"key": "no_unauthorized_advice", "name": "No unauthorised investment advice", "weight": 2.0, "category": "compliance", "severity": "critical", "score_type": "pass_fail", "description": "The broker must not give unsolicited investment advice, price predictions, or buy/sell recommendations. Factual information (current price, order status, product features) is allowed. Fail if the broker volunteers recommendations or predictions."}, {"key": "risk_disclosure", "name": "Risk disclosure where required", "weight": 1.0, "category": "compliance", "severity": "warning", "score_type": "pass_fail", "description": "If the client asks for an opinion, or the order involves derivatives or leveraged products, the broker must give an appropriate risk warning. For plain equity orders where no advice is sought, this criterion passes by default."}, {"key": "professional_conduct", "name": "Professional conduct", "weight": 1.0, "category": "quality", "severity": "info", "score_type": "scale_1_5", "description": "The broker is courteous and professional throughout: a proper greeting identifying the firm, polite tone, no over-familiarity that compromises professionalism, and a proper closing. Score 1 (poor) to 5 (exemplary)."}]	[{"key": "stock_code", "label": "Stock code", "scope": "trade", "field_type": "string", "enum_options": null}, {"key": "stock_name", "label": "Stock name", "scope": "trade", "field_type": "string", "enum_options": null}, {"key": "side", "label": "Side", "scope": "trade", "field_type": "enum", "enum_options": ["buy", "sell", "amend", "cancel", "unknown"]}, {"key": "quantity", "label": "Quantity", "scope": "trade", "field_type": "number", "enum_options": null}, {"key": "price", "label": "Price", "scope": "trade", "field_type": "number", "enum_options": null}, {"key": "price_type", "label": "Price type", "scope": "trade", "field_type": "enum", "enum_options": ["market", "limit", "unknown"]}, {"key": "client_name", "label": "Client name", "scope": "trade", "field_type": "string", "enum_options": null}, {"key": "client_account", "label": "Client account", "scope": "trade", "field_type": "string", "enum_options": null}, {"key": "call_purpose", "label": "Call purpose", "scope": "call", "field_type": "enum", "enum_options": ["place_order", "amend_or_cancel", "inquiry", "complaint", "other"]}, {"key": "complaint_mentioned", "label": "Complaint mentioned", "scope": "call", "field_type": "boolean", "enum_options": null}]	The client, Mr. Wong, called to place a buy order for Alibaba. The broker accepted a limit order to buy 300 shares of Alibaba at HKD 153.7. However, the broker failed 